{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So I grew up in Limpopo, on the border of Limpopo"},{"time":3059,"text":"and Mpumalanga, a little town called Motetema."},{"time":6068,"text":"Water and electricity supply are as unpredictable"},{"time":8621,"text":"as the weather, and growing up in these tough situations,"},{"time":12890,"text":"at the age of 17, I was relaxing with a couple of friends"},{"time":16413,"text":"of mine in winter, and we were sunbathing."},{"time":18959,"text":"The Limpopo sun gets really hot in winter."},{"time":22148,"text":"So as we were sunbathing, my best friend next to me says,"},{"time":25332,"text":"\"Man, why doesn't somebody invent something that you can"},{"time":28381,"text":"just put on your skin and then you don't have to bathe?\""},{"time":32115,"text":"And I sat, and I was like, \"Man, I would buy that, eh?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":36026,"text":"So I went home, and I did a little research,"},{"time":39561,"text":"and I found some very shocking statistics."},{"time":42993,"text":"Over 2.5 billion people in the world today"},{"time":46010,"text":"do not have proper access to water and sanitation."},{"time":49011,"text":"Four hundred and fifty million of them are in Africa,"},{"time":51134,"text":"and five million of them are in South Africa."},{"time":53901,"text":"Various diseases thrive in this environment,"},{"time":56441,"text":"the most drastic of which is called trachoma."},{"time":59788,"text":"Trachoma is an infection of the eye due to dirt"},{"time":62589,"text":"getting into your eye. Multiple infections of trachoma"},{"time":65898,"text":"can leave you permanently blind."},{"time":68582,"text":"The disease leaves eight million people permanently blind"},{"time":72315,"text":"each and every year. The shocking part about it"},{"time":75060,"text":"is that to avoid being infected with trachoma,"},{"time":77757,"text":"all you have to do is wash your face:"},{"time":79630,"text":"no medicine, no pills, no injections."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82443,"text":"So after seeing these shocking statistics, I thought to myself,"},{"time":85346,"text":"\"Okay, even if I'm not just doing it for myself"},{"time":87698,"text":"and the fact that I don't want to bathe, I at least need"},{"time":90411,"text":"to do it to try to save the world.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":93051,"text":"So with my trusty little steed, my Nokia 6234 cell phone --"},{"time":98004,"text":"I didn't have a laptop, I didn't have Internet much,"},{"time":100859,"text":"except for the 20-rand-an-hour Internet cafe —"},{"time":103804,"text":"I did research on Wikipedia, on Google, about lotions,"},{"time":106845,"text":"creams, the compositions, the melting points, the toxicities --"},{"time":110582,"text":"I did high school science --"},{"time":112110,"text":"and I wrote down a little formula on a piece of paper,"},{"time":115848,"text":"and it looked like the KFC special spice, you know?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119220,"text":"So I was like, okay, so we've got the formula ready."},{"time":121709,"text":"Now we need to get this thing into practice."},{"time":124458,"text":"Fast forward four years later, after having written"},{"time":128454,"text":"a 40-page business plan on the cell phone,"},{"time":131038,"text":"having written my patent on the cell phone,"},{"time":133137,"text":"I'm the youngest patent-holder in the country,"},{"time":135830,"text":"and — (\"No more bathing!\") —"},{"time":138731,"text":"I can't say any more than that. (Laughter)"},{"time":141336,"text":"I had invented DryBath, the world's first"},{"time":145078,"text":"bath-substituting lotion."},{"time":147864,"text":"You literally put it on your skin, and you don't have to bathe."},{"time":152197,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156582,"text":"So after having tried to make it work in high school"},{"time":159271,"text":"with the limited resources I had, I went to university,"},{"time":162788,"text":"met a few people, got it into practice,"},{"time":165491,"text":"and we have a fully functioning product that's ready"},{"time":168543,"text":"to go to the market. It's actually available on the market."},{"time":171340,"text":"So we learned a few lessons in commercializing"},{"time":174266,"text":"and making DryBath available."},{"time":176693,"text":"One of the things we learned was that poor communities"},{"time":179049,"text":"don't buy products in bulk."},{"time":181309,"text":"They buy products on demand. A person in Alex"},{"time":183786,"text":"doesn't buy a box of cigarettes. They buy one cigarette"},{"time":186180,"text":"each day, even though it's more expensive."},{"time":188590,"text":"So we packaged DryBath in these innovative little sachets."},{"time":191236,"text":"You just snap them in half, and you squeeze it out."},{"time":194126,"text":"And the cool part is, one sachet substitutes one bath"},{"time":197813,"text":"for five rand."},{"time":200023,"text":"After creating that model, we also learned a lot"},{"time":202715,"text":"in terms of implementing the product."},{"time":204456,"text":"We realized that even rich kids from the suburbs"},{"time":206774,"text":"really want DryBath. (Laughter)"},{"time":208962,"text":"At least once a week."},{"time":211145,"text":"Anyway, we realized that we could save 80 million liters"},{"time":213757,"text":"of water on average each time they skipped a bath,"},{"time":216888,"text":"and also we would save two hours a day for kids"},{"time":219823,"text":"who are in rural areas, two hours more for school,"},{"time":222889,"text":"two hours more for homework,"},{"time":224673,"text":"two hours more to just be a kid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227521,"text":"After seeing that global impact, we narrowed it down"},{"time":230168,"text":"to our key value proposition,"},{"time":232532,"text":"which was cleanliness and convenience."},{"time":234775,"text":"DryBath is a rich man's convenience"},{"time":237407,"text":"and a poor man's lifesaver."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239777,"text":"Having put the product into practice, we are actually now"},{"time":243249,"text":"on the verge of selling the product"},{"time":245293,"text":"onto a multinational to take it to the retail market,"},{"time":248406,"text":"and one question I have for the audience today is,"},{"time":251931,"text":"on the gravel roads of Limpopo,"},{"time":254204,"text":"with an allowance of 50 rand a week,"},{"time":257553,"text":"I came up with a way for the world not to bathe."},{"time":261375,"text":"What's stopping you? (Applause)"},{"time":264083,"text":"I'm not done yet. I'm not done yet."},{"time":267029,"text":"And another key thing that I learned a lot"},{"time":270094,"text":"throughout this whole process,"},{"time":271442,"text":"last year Google named me as one of the brightest young minds in the world."},{"time":275527,"text":"I'm also currently the best student entrepreneur"},{"time":278396,"text":"in the world, the first African to get that accolade,"},{"time":281152,"text":"and one thing that really puzzles me is, I did all of this"},{"time":286147,"text":"just because I didn't want to bathe. Thank you."},{"time":289783,"text":"(Applause.)"}]}]}